data.description: Prime Location Church Lake property with Private boat launch, 100' no bank Lake Tapps waterfront, brand new dock, 180°+ unobstructed lake view, deck, .30 acre lot, 3120 sq ft, Mt Rainier view from Master & partial view from upstairs bedroom, new roof, fresh exterior paint, hardwood flooring on upper & tile downstairs, triple pane windows, private park access, huge garage with shop & storage room, extra-large utility/mud room. Hydro-baseboard heating & two fireplaces! Firepit, RV parking. Great location within minutes to shops, restaurants & highway 410.
